items.title: Indians or Dodgers: Which streak is less likely?
items.summary: Cleveland is running a streak of 18 straight wins, but the Dodgers have lost 10 in a row and 15 of 16. Which streak is less likely? Running the numbers shows that the odds against either one of these runs are massive.
